"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"I spoke with a well-regarded colleague of mine about the Crypto market as a whole, we discussed the cool things like NFTs, Metaverse and the proliferation of DAOs. But it struck me that although these “headline topics” have become a part of the mainstream part of discourse, there is still a huge knowledge gap of how these technologies are developed and what the drivers are of them. In this piece, I dive into a surface-level introduction of what Ethereum is and why you should care about it.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/tx645H1q6mhgrvZscno9N.JPG?height=720&width=1280)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/CMyyDz-sfu-23nrnILbg5.JPG?height=720&width=1280)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/6SJVVr3VcQ6aJ8htMGijs.JPG?height=720&width=1280)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/fo8xnV1RnZkAyaY25KBVZ.JPG?height=720&width=1280)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/_t5WnMoSMq8lwtto5KXcT.JPG?height=720&width=1280)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/szxuQ9tVfo4PdIB_rZwYn.JPG?height=720&width=1280)\\n\\nNote that none of the above headlines would be possible without Ethereum. Ethereum is the electricity that powers our lightbulbs per se. It’s enabled the $40bn DeFi market, the \\\\~$10bn in YTD NFT trade volume and is what’s fueling the growth of web3.\",\"timestamp\":1634533274,\"title\":\"Why You Should Care About Ethereum if You Don’t Already\"},\"digest\":\"9DLnd3InTIrRdDvbG--_AJbBOwrBhsgpE63yUWV167k\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x23bdEb4396BEB7e179c65A3FcA025EA2ABC156D5\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"K0LHzJS2zlzRKk50GszQsxk0m5v3PPiAqJIoy3Ejl2I\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"kBvI26SZ8NDksrjvRSf3CdEQ04zCtWYd7LEzfMRGoQc\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"6qpUDP3usPnW9zjUwQdSURRGfgtXU_JPucgXCdZHLl52_YGmwZ6DkEu6xNdmZmyccLRm7U